íticos argumentar que muchas personas transgénero se arrepienten de su decisión de someterse a operaciones quirúrgicas de reasignación de sexo, una creencia que ha estado alimentando una oleada legislativa que restringen el acceso a la atencióne sanitaria de afirmación de género.\n\nLa...","byline":"Harry Barbee, Johns Hopkins University; Bashar Hassan, Johns Hopkins University, and Fan Liang, Johns Hopkins University","contentType":"analysis","hideByline":false,"image":{"src":"https://images.theconversation.com/files/575703/original/file-20240115-19-obyz75.jpg","alt":"Una joven se pinta los labios.","placeholderColor":"#522d31","paletteData":{"averageLuminance":0.118709},"crops":[{"type":"free","width":5179,"height":3519,"x":135,"y":23},{"type":"square","width":3064,"height":3064,"x":1085,"y":0},{"type":"landscape","width":3782,"height":2521,"x":646,"y":0},{"type":"pano","width":4086,"height":2043,"x":0,"y":0}]}}],"slotSizes":["LG","BASE","BASE","BASE","BASE"],"columns":4},{"type":"CALL_TO_ACTION","props":{"href":"https://theconversation.com/es/republishing-guidelines","text":"Normas de republicación","style":"DEFAULT","title":""},"href":"https://theconversation.com/es/republishing-guidelines","title":"","text":"Normas de republicación","style":"DEFAULT"},{"type":"HEADING","props":{"text":"Salud","level":2}},{"type":"GRID","props":{"blocks":[{"type":"CONTENT_SUMMARY","props":{"id":"213461","tagLabel":"","tagStyle":"NONE","customTitle":""}},{"type":"CONTENT_SUMMARY","props":{"id":"221286","tagLabel":"","tagStyle":"NONE","customTitle":""}},{"type":"CONTENT_SUMMARY","props":{"id":"216880","tagLabel":"","tagStyle":"NONE","customTitle":""}},{"type":"CONTENT_SUMMARY","props":{"id":"202423","tagLabel":"","tagStyle":"NONE","customTitle":""}},{"type":"CONTENT_SUMMARY","props":{"id":"202290","tagLabel":"","tagStyle":"NONE","customTitle":""}}],"columns":4,"slotSizes":["LG","BASE","BASE","BASE","BASE"]},"blocks":[{"type":"CONTENT_SUMMARY","id":"213461","url":"https://theconver